Vagrant
What is vagrant? what is the purpose of it?
Vagrant is an virtualization workflow automation tool that can be used by developers, quality assurance engineers and the support/operational engineers in developing and delivering the software applications

Why do we need virtualization & workflow automation tool for virtualization?
There are 2 questions here
1. why do we need virtualization?
2. why do we need an workflow automation tool for virtualization?
	
